</sect2>

<sect2 id="misc-tools">
<title>Miscellaneous Tools</title>

<para>The move tool
<guiicon>
<inlinemediaobject>
<imageobject><imagedata fileref="move.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Move Tool</phrase></textobject>
</inlinemediaobject>
</guiicon>
moves the individual layers of the image. If your drawing on the top
layer is not quite aligned with the drawings on lower layers, then the
move tool can be used to adjust the top layer.</para>

<para>The zoom tool
<guiicon>
<inlinemediaobject>
<imageobject><imagedata fileref="viewmag.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Zoom Tool</phrase></textobject>
</inlinemediaobject>
</guiicon>
</para>

<para>The color picker
<guiicon>
<inlinemediaobject>
<imageobject><imagedata fileref="colorpicker.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Color Picker</phrase></textobject>
